    "body": "I try the following code with Mercator projection and it works \r\n\r\n```\r\ngmt coast -RUY -JM-50/-40/6c -Bfg -Gspringgreen -Sazure -N1 -png GMT_cassini \r\n```\r\n\r\nbut when I change to Cassini it fails and get this error message:\r\n\r\n```\r\ngmt coast -RUY -JC-50/-40/6c -Bfg -Gspringgreen -Sazure -N1 -png GMT_cassini\r\n\r\ncoast [ERROR]: Max longitude extension away from central meridian is limited to +/- 90 degrees\r\ncoast [ERROR]: General map projection error\r\n```\r\n\r\nIf I use a region with WESN then it works:\r\n\r\n`gmt coast -R-59/-53/-35/-30 -JC-50/-40/6c -Bfg -Gspringgreen -Sazure -N1 -png GMT_cassini`\r\n\r\n\r\n![GMT_cassini](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/17908951/136304896-8dfcfac3-ad2b-489d-9a06-ba3a0121b7d0.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n",
